mmanuel Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 663, \"end\": 668, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.711748477203269e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 698, \"end\": 709, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"score\": 0.9791047767540926, \"rank\": 0.019644741739865718, \"text\": \"Saint-Denis\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the success\", \"from\": 468, \"to\": 479}, {\"ngram\": \"this project\", \"from\": 483, \"to\": 495}, {\"ngram\": \"seven years\", \"from\": 506, \"to\": 517}, {\"ngram\": \"almost 82 buildings\", \"from\": 541, \"to\": 560}, {\"ngram\": \"3,000 apartments\", \"from\": 562, \"to\": 578}, {\"ngram\": \"7,200 rooms\", \"from\": 583, \"to\": 594}, {\"ngram\": \"a plot\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 605}, {\"ngram\": \"land\", \"from\": 609, \"to\": 613}, {\"ngram\": \"over 52 hectares\", \"from\": 629, \"to\": 645}, {\"ngram\": \"the north\", \"from\": 650, \"to\": 659}, {\"ngram\": \"Saint-Denis\", \"from\": 678, \"to\": 689}, {\"ngram\": \"Saint-Ouen\", \"from\": 714, \"to\": 724}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The work for the reception of the 206 Olympic delegates will not end tomorrow, the organizers will have to work for the next five months because the delivered apartments are empty, and now they will have to be equipped, the furniture installed (beds, bedside tables, etc.)\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 998, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The work\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 734}, {\"ngram\": \"the reception\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 752}, {\"ngram\": \"the 206 Olympic delegates\", \"from\": 756, \"to\": 781}, {\"ngram\": \"the organizers\", \"from\": 805, \"to\": 819}, {\"ngram\": \"the next five months\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 862}, {\"ngram\": \"the delivered apartments\", \"from\": 871, \"to\": 895}, {\"ngram\": \"the furniture\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 959}, {\"ngram\": \"beds\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 975}, {\"ngram\": \"bedside tables\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 991}]}, {\"sentence\": \"and service centers for athletes set up .\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1040, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"and service centers\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1018}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1031}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This represents more than 345,000 pieces in total, which will be transported.\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1120, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more than 345,000 pieces\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1083}, {\"ngram\": \"total\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1092}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There will be 14,250 duvets, bedside tables, beds, we will have 8,200 fans and 5,535 sofas,\\\" said Laurent Michand, director of the Olympic and Paralympic Villages at Paris-2024.\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1298, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"14,250 duvets\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1148}, {\"ngram\": \"bedside tables\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1164}, {\"ngram\": \"beds\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1170}, {\"ngram\": \"8,200 fans\", \"from\": 1185, \"to\": 1195}, {\"ngram\": \"5,535 sofas\", \"from\": 1200, \"to\": 1211}, {\"ngram\": \"Laurent Michand\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1234}, {\"ngram\": \"director\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1244}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic and Paralympic Villages\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1283}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris-2024\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1297}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There will be two athletes in a room of 12 square meters and a bathroom for four people.\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1388, \"entitie