ntence\": \"Athletes will be able, for example, to wash their clothes in temporary laundromats, with nearly 600 washing machines and dryers available.\", \"from\": 1723, \"to\": 1861, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Athletes\", \"from\": 1723, \"to\": 1731}, {\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1757}, {\"ngram\": \"their clothes\", \"from\": 1767, \"to\": 1780}, {\"ngram\": \"temporary laundromats\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1805}, {\"ngram\": \"nearly 600 washing machines\", \"from\": 1812, \"to\": 1839}, {\"ngram\": \"dryers\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 1850}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The maintenance of the apartments in over 70 residences will be provided by 12 specialized services scattered throughout the Village.\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 1995, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The maintenance\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 1877}, {\"ngram\": \"the apartments\", \"from\": 1881, \"to\": 1895}, {\"ngram\": \"over 70 residences\", \"from\": 1899, \"to\": 1917}, {\"ngram\": \"12 specialized services\", \"from\": 1938, \"to\": 1961}, {\"ngram\": \"the Village\", \"from\": 1983, \"to\": 1994}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Only the kitchens will be missing from the apartments.\", \"from\": 1996, \"to\": 2050, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Only the kitchens\", \"from\": 1996, \"to\": 2013}, {\"ngram\": \"the apartments\", \"from\": 2035, \"to\": 2049}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The athletes will have 24-hour access to a giant restaurant, with a choice of six culinary themes (Italy, Asia, France, etc.)\", \"from\": 2051, \"to\": 2176, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2150, \"end\": 2155, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 2.3715175023704227e-12, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}, {\"begin\": 2163, \"end\": 2169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\